        "created_at": "2017-12-01T16:36:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Interestingly, I saw an offer for some DdCdM wines just yesterday, claiming they have really elevated their game. I haven\u2019t had any in over 20 years. My first \u201cvisit\u201d to Burgundy was an overnight stop driving from Paris to Zurich in about 1995. Saw signs for CdM, and stopped for their tour/tasting. Which was interesting, if uninspiring.</p>",
